    "body": "This issue can be reproduced at [repo](https://github.com/hiroshitash/hardhat-duplicate-block-event). \r\n\r\nAn issue was created at [ethers.js](https://github.com/ethers-io/ethers.js/issues/4113). This issue stems from different implementations between WebSocketProvider and JsonRpcProvider in ethers.js on version 5.5.4. Please see [the issue](https://github.com/ethers-io/ethers.js/issues/4113) in ethers.js for more detail.",
